WEBVTT

00:05:57.320 --> 00:06:00.576
For free Wi-Fi, do not
so easily give out your details;

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:02.696
there are hosts of ways
to keep them hidden.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:04.256
One of them is VPN,

00:06:04.280 --> 00:06:07.696
through this you can
secretly surf the internet.

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:13.656
What is important here is that we discuss
these everyday with children.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.976
Surf the internet jointly with them.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.336
Trust me, you will learn a lot.

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:21.976
Tell them that they should
delete emails from strangers.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.440
They should not meet strangers

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:25.970
who they have met
for the first time only online.

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:32.456
I think that figuring out relationships
and trust issues only in the real world